---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Legal Disclaimer | ARM Management"
  description="Legal disclaimer for arm-management.com — nature of advisory, regulatory status, and limitations of information published on this website."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40vh">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829545856-d10d557cf95f?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Legal Disclaimer</h1>
      <p>The nature of ARM Management's advisory and the limitations of information published on this website.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#9CA3AF;margin-bottom:40px">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:24px">Nature of Advisory</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management is an independent international business advisory. Nothing published on this website, and nothing communicated by ARM Management before a formal service agreement is signed, constitutes regulated investment advice, legal advice, financial advice, tax advice, or immigration advice.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px">ARM Management is not a law firm, a regulated financial adviser, a licensed immigration adviser, or a registered tax agent in any jurisdiction. Where engagements require regulated professional services, ARM Management coordinates with appropriately licensed local professionals on behalf of clients.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">Information on This Website</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">The information published on arm-management.com is provided for general informational purposes only. It does not constitute, and should not be relied upon as, professional advice of any kind. Regulatory requirements, tax regimes, corporate laws, and visa programmes described on this website are subject to change, and may vary significantly by jurisdiction and individual circumstance.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px">ARM Management makes reasonable efforts to ensure information is current and accurate, but makes no representations or warranties as to its completeness, accuracy, or fitness for any particular purpose. You should obtain appropriate professional advice specific to your situation before taking any action based on information published on this website.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">Jurisdiction-Specific Limitations</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">The information and services described on this website may not be available in all jurisdictions. References to specific regulatory frameworks, licensing regimes, or programme requirements are provided for general information only and do not constitute an offer to provide services in any particular jurisdiction.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px">In particular, ARM Management does not provide regulated financial services, investment advice, or legal advice in the United Kingdom, the United States, the European Union, or any other jurisdiction without appropriate local regulatory authorisation. Clients in regulated jurisdictions are advised to consult appropriately authorised professionals for advice in those areas.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">No Client Relationship</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Viewing this website, submitting an enquiry, or conducting an initial consultation with ARM Management does not create a client relationship or any professional obligation. A client relationship is created only upon execution of a formal, written service agreement signed by both parties.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, ARM Management accepts no liability for any loss or damage (including indirect or consequential loss) arising from reliance on information published on this website or from the use of this website. ARM Management's liability in respect of any formal engagement is governed exclusively by the terms of the relevant service agreement.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">Third-Party Links</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">This website may contain links to third-party websites. ARM Management has no control over the content of those sites and accepts no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from your use of them.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:56px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6" class="reveal">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
